dc_title_s: Tokyô oyobi Yokohama fukkô chizu Jiji Shinpôsha.
dc_description_s: Jiji Shinpô furoku. [Appendix to Jiji Shinpô.] "Fukkôkyoku kônin." [Authorized by Restoration Bureau.] In Japanese. North oriented toward right. Includes inset, legend and rebuilding plan list. On verso: 18 maps collectively entitled "Tokyô-shi sûyô chiku shindôro kakudaizu." Edited by Ishikawa Renjô. 1 map: col.; 74 x 91 cm., in wrapper 28 x 21 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
